<!-- File: public/icons/dog-anim.svg -->
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 120 120" class="dog-icon">
  <!-- Cabeça -->
  <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="50" fill="#f5d7b2" stroke="#000" stroke-width="3"/>

  <!-- Orelhas -->
  <ellipse cx="25" cy="35" rx="15" ry="25" fill="#c49a6c" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2"/>
  <ellipse cx="95" cy="35" rx="15" ry="25" fill="#c49a6c" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2"/>

  <!-- Olhos -->
  <circle class="eye left-eye" cx="40" cy="55" r="8" fill="#000"/>
  <circle class="eye right-eye" cx="80" cy="55" r="8" fill="#000"/>

  <!-- Boca -->
  <path d="M45 80 Q60 95 75 80" stroke="#000" stroke-width="3" fill="transparent"/>

  <!-- Língua -->
  <path class="tongue" d="M58 82 Q60 105 62 82 Z" fill="#ff6b6b" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1"/>
</svg>
